(41, 4, 9, 41, 7, 14, 15, 'He that hath ears to hear', 'Hearing and Understanding', 'This connection highlights the importance of listening and understanding in both passages. In Mark 4:9, the call to ''hear'' is echoed in Mark 7:14, where the emphasis is on understanding what is being communicated.', 'theme', 0.34199999999999997, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
(41, 4, 9, 42, 8, 18, 18, 'He that hath ears to hear', 'Hearing and Understanding', 'Both passages emphasize the importance of how one hears. Mark 4:9''s call to ''hear'' connects to Luke 8:18''s warning to ''take heed how ye hear,'' suggesting that the manner of listening affects understanding and retention.', 'theme', 0.34199999999999997, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
