(41, 4, 10, 40, 13, 36, 36, 'asked of him the parable', 'Disciples'' Inquiry About Parables', 'Both passages emphasize the disciples'' desire for understanding of Jesus'' parables. In Mark, they ask about the parable, while in Matthew, they specifically request clarification on the parable of the tares.', 'theme', 0.321, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
